'''Ian Adams''' is a peds patient who struggled to find a Halloween costume.

==History==
Ian found Levi and asked for his help picking a Halloween costume. Levi went through the options, but Ian didn't want any of them. When Levi asked him what he wanted to be, he said he wanted to be a sunflower. Levi made two sunflower costumes, one for himself and one for Ian, which he wore to the costume parade.
